  </sponsors>
  <source>3M</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To establish the clinical test performance characteristics of sensitivity, specificity and
      predictive values for direct detection of nasal Staphylococcus aureus colonization against
      clinical microbiology laboratory culture methods.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
